<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-1940] Faulty pdf-&gt;image rendering</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1940</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A particular PDF is producing improper output jpg.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The pdf in question, as well as the produced jpg can be found attached to this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
